        "header_title": "Protecting Your <em>Privacy and Security</em>",
        "header_description": "<p>We prioritize your privacy at every step. Our devices use end-to-end encryption and secure data practices to ensure your information is protected.</p><p>Only the data you choose is collected, and you can review, manage, or delete it at any time, giving you full control over your information.</p><p>Keep your home and family's information safe while letting you enjoy smart technology with peace of mind.</p>",
